messages.messageBody: How much extra would it cost to get full replacement on the roof?
Noah, just noticed that the policy Coverage A - Dwelling is for $585,000.  We are buying the house for $870,000.

Noah, yes I received your email and will look over the quote.
The loan company is requiring the insurance company to have a minimum of an A rating.  And that the policy covers full replacement cost.  Can you let me know if we meet both of those items?
Happy to talk through it to make sure that is the case.
I did receive it. The video was a bit frustrating. I think my current insurance policy is better and less expensive than what you quoted.
